\c 17
\s Nhaka yaManase
\p
\v 1 Kwakavawo nemujenya werudzi rwaManase, nokuti waiva dangwe raJosefa, \add waiva\add* waMakiri dangwe raManase baba vaGiriyadhi, nokuti iye waiva munhu wehondo, naizvozvo wakava neGiriyadhi neBhashani.
\v 2 Kwaivawo neyevakasara vevanakomana vaManase zvichienderana nemhuri dzavo, yevana vaAbhiezeri, neyevana vaHereki, neyevana vaAsirieri, neyevana vaShekemu, neyevana vaHeferi, neyevana vaShemidha. Ava vana vanhurume vaManase mwanakomana waJosefa zvichienderana nemhuri dzavo.
\p
\v 3 Asi Zerofehadhi mwanakomana waHeferi mwanakomana waGiriyadhi mwanakomana waMakiri mwanakomana waManase waiva asina vanakomana, asi vanasikana. Zvino awa mazita evanasikana vake: Mahira, naNowa, Hogira, Mirika, naTiriza.
\v 4 Zvino vakaswedera pamberi paEriazari mupristi nepamberi paJoshua mwanakomana waNuni nepamberi pemachinda vachiti: Jehovha wakaraira Mozisi kutipa nhaka pakati pehama dzedu. Zvino wakavapa zvichienderana nemurairo waJehovha nhaka pakati pehama dzababa vavo.
\v 5 Naizvozvo kwakawira mijenya gumi kuna Manase, kunze kwenyika yeGiriyadhi neBhashani dziri mhiri kwaJoridhani.
\v 6 Nokuti vanasikana vaManase vakagara nhaka pakati pevanakomana vake. Uye nyika yeGiriyadhi yaiva yevakasara vevanakomana vaManase.
\p
\v 7 Zvino muganhu waManase waiva kubva paAsheri kuenda kuMikimetati riri pamberi peShekemu; muganhu ndokuenderera kurudyi, kusvika kuvagari veEni-Tapua.
\v 8 Nyika yeTapua yakava kuna Manase; asi Tapua pamuganhu waManase yakava kuvana vaEfuremu.
\v 9 Zvino muganhu wakaburukira kurwizi Kana nechekuchamhembe kwerwizi. Maguta awa ndeaEfuremu pakati pemaguta aManase. Uye muganhu waManase waiva kumaodzanyemba kwerwizi; uye kubuda kwawo kwaiva pagungwa.
\v 10 Kuchamhembe yaiva yaEfuremu, uye kumaodzanyemba yaiva yaManase; uye gungwa waiva muganhu wake; uye kuna Asheri vaisangana kumaodzanyemba, nekuna Isasikari kumabvazuva.
\v 11 Nokuti kuna Isasikari nekuna Asheri Manase waiva neBheti-Sheani nemisha yaro, neIbhireami nemisha yaro, nevagari veDhori nemisha yaro, nevagari veEndori nemisha yaro, nevagari veTaanaki nemisha yaro, nevagari veMegidho nemisha yaro: Nzvimbo nhatu dzezvikomo.
\v 12 Asi vana vaManase vaiva vasingagoni kudzinga panhaka yemaguta iwawo; asi vaKenani vaida kugara panyika iyo.
\v 13 Zvino zvakaitika vana vaIsraeri pavakava vane simba, kuti vakabatisa vaKenani chibharo, asi havana kuvadzinga zvachose.
\p
\v 14 Zvino vana vaJosefa vakataura naJoshua vachiti: Makatipirei mujenya umwe nemugove umwe kuva nhaka, zvandiri rudzi rukuru, Jehovha sezvaakandiropafadza kusvika pano?
\v 15 Joshua ndokuti kwavari: Kana uri rudzi rukuru, zvikwirire kudondo, unozvitemerapo panyika yevaPerezi neyeVaRefaimu, kana gomo reEfuremu rakamanikana kwauri.
\v 16 Zvino vana vaJosefa vakati: Chikomo hachitikwaniri, uye vaKenani vose vanogara munyika yemupata vane ngoro dzematare, nevari paBheti-Sheani nemisha yaro, nevari mumupata weJezireeri.
\v 17 Zvino Joshua wakataura kune veimba yaJosefa, kuna Efuremu nekuna Manase achiti: Uri rudzi rukuru, uye une simba guru; haungavi nemujenya umwe chete;
\v 18 asi gomo richava rako, nokuti idondo, ucharitema; uye kubuda kwaro kuve kwako; nokuti uchadzinga vaKenani kunyange vane ngoro dzematare, kunyange vane simba.
